cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO) sub-categories as it deals with LiDAR sensors and cameras, which are commonly used in autonomous driving and UAVs. The paper also proposes a deep learning framework for point cloud interpolation, which falls under the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Finally, the paper may also be relevant to the graphics (cs.GR) sub-category as it deals with generating 3D point clouds.
